## Success Messages
- **Upload successful** → "Yükleme başarılı"
- **File saved** → "Dosya kaydedildi"
- **Changes applied** → "Değişiklikler uygulandı"
- **Operation completed** → "İşlem tamamlandı"

## Critical Rules
- ✅ All user-facing text must be in Turkish
- ✅ Technical terms (ROAS, Dashboard) can remain in English
- ✅ Error messages must be user-friendly in Turkish
- ✅ Button labels must be clear and concise
- ✅ Data labels must be consistent across all components
- ✅ Use proper Turkish grammar and spelling